message.entry: The Method property value is invalid.
Number of elements must be an integer.
Multiplicative factor must be an odd integer.
Multiplicative factor must be greater than zero.
Multiplicative factor must be less than Number of elements.
Cyclic shift must be an integer.
Cyclic shift must be greater than or equal to zero.
Cyclic shift must be less than Number of elements.
Primitive element must be less than Number of elements.
Specified value is not a primitive element.
